dct_title_s: Lakes and Ponds Door County, Wisconsin 2010
dct_description_sm: This polygon data layer represents lakes and ponds for Door County, Wisconsin in 2010. The dataset was originally published by the Door County Land Information office in June 2010.[Lakes-Ponds_swi2 was derived from Surface Water Inventory of Door County - December 2000. Source files includied hydrogrpahic features collected as part of 1994 digital base map project.]
dct_creator_sm: Door County Soil and Water Conservation Department
